-- Quiet or Die module for Serenity. Standalone, like UE -- no shared runtime/theme table
-- to hook into, so this builds its own small panel matching the hub's look. Ported from
-- the old hub's QOD page: Auto Kill, Auto Farm (+ Safe Place, Mute Audio, tucked behind an
-- Edit button so the main panel stays uncluttered), Auto Revive, Auto Event (also behind
-- Edit), and an ESP toggle that labels whoever's currently the killer. The old hub's
-- ThemeObjects/HubState wiring, keybind rebinding, persistent execution-history panel,
-- Coins/Wins readout, and Auto Reveal were all dropped -- toggles are plain click buttons.
local Players = game:GetService("Players")
local RunService = game:GetService("RunService")
local UserInputService = game:GetService("UserInputService")
